            "title": "欧洲股市早段上升",
            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">&lt;汇港通讯&gt;     欧洲股市早段上升。英国富时100指数报9,571.83点，升64.42点(0.68%)；德国DAX指数报23,416.42点，升253.50点(1.09%)；法国CAC 40指数报8,055.81点，升102.04点(1.28%)。 <br/>(WL)</span>\n</div>",
